characteristics.name: Capacity
characteristics.value: This model can transport 10 <Legion> or <Mark of Chaos> Infantry models. Each JUMP PACK or TERMINATOR model takes the space of two other models. This model can instead transport a single HELLFORGED CONTEMPTOR DREADNOUGHT, CHAOS DECIMATOR or HELBRUTE, and no other models. It cannot transport a HELLFORGED LEVIATHAN DREADNOUGHT or HELLFORGED DEREDEO DREADNOUGHT.
